race.description: South Coast Greenwell Point Cup Hcp (Bm66)
race.comment: Raced has been knocked about by scratchings which now sees MISS SCOOP (6) as the clear top pick. Resumes for Joseph-Jones and is proven fresh. Has won this track/trip and Collett is a positive jockey engagement. Good enough to beat these rivals fresh. PRINCESS HALO (1) resumed in tougher at Canberra and needed the outing. Has placed in two of three second-up attempts so should have come on. Looks the danger. MOTORBOAT (8) is the outsider of the small field but draws on the fence and did manage a placing at Canberra three back.
